《'''我英勇的爱人'''》（{{lang-ga|Mo Ghile Mear}}；{{lang-en|My Gallant Darling}}）是一首[[爱尔兰|爱尔兰]]民歌，作者是18世纪的{{link-en|肖恩·克拉拉赫·麥克·當勞|Seán Clárach Mac Domhnaill}}。<ref>{{cite magazine |date=24 December 1994 |title=Hail to the Chieftains |url=http://books.google.ie/books?id=ZAgEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA14&dq=%22ghile+mear%22+Domhnaill&hl=en&sa=X&ei=x_ufU4HCEsmr7AaWs4CACA&ved=0CCgQ6AEwAg#v=onepage&q=%22ghile%20mear%22%20Domhnaill&f=false |journal=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|告示牌 (雜誌)]] |publisher=Nielsen Business Media, Inc |pages=14 |doi= |accessdate=17 June 2014 |archive-date=2014-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141224152555/http://books.google.ie/books?id=ZAgEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA14&dq=%22ghile+mear%22+Domhnaill&hl=en&sa=X&ei=x_ufU4HCEsmr7AaWs4CACA&ved=0CCgQ6AEwAg#v=onepage&q=%22ghile%20mear%22%20Domhnaill&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>

这首歌是按照“{{link-en|阿詩灵|Aisling}}”诗（献给盖尔女神{{link-en|爱尔尤|Ériu}}的輓歌）的格式写成，为当时流亡在外的[[英国|英国]][[詹姆斯党|詹姆斯党]]王位宣称者[[查尔斯·爱德华·斯图亚特|英俊王子查理]]而作。<ref>{{cite journal|title= Traditional Irish folk music, the Ó Domhnaill family, and contemporary song accompaniments |author= William David Coulter |publisher=University of California |date=1994 |page=79 }}</ref>

